{"id":37,"ayahs":[{"number":231,"arabic":"وَإِذَا طَلَّقْتُمُ ٱلنِّسَآءَ فَبَلَغْنَ أَجَلَهُنَّ فَأَمْسِكُوهُنَّ بِمَعْرُوفٍ أَوْ سَرِّحُوهُنَّ بِمَعْرُوفٍۢ ۚ وَلَا تُمْسِكُوهُنَّ ضِرَارًۭا لِّتَعْتَدُوا۟ ۚ وَمَن يَفْعَلْ ذَٰلِكَ فَقَدْ ظَلَمَ نَفْسَهُۥ ۚ وَلَا تَتَّخِذُوٓا۟ ءَايَٰتِ ٱللَّهِ هُزُوًۭا ۚ وَٱذْكُرُوا۟ نِعْمَتَ ٱللَّهِ عَلَيْكُمْ وَمَآ أَنزَلَ عَلَيْكُم مِّنَ ٱلْكِتَٰبِ وَٱلْحِكْمَةِ يَعِظُكُم بِهِۦ ۚ وَٱتَّقُوا۟ ٱللَّهَ وَٱعْلَمُوٓا۟ أَنَّ ٱللَّهَ بِكُلِّ شَىْءٍ عَلِيمٌۭ","translation":"And so, when you divorce women and they are about to reach the end of their waiting-term, then either retain them in a fair manner or let them go in a fair manner. But do not retain them against their will in order to hurt [them]: for he who does so sins indeed against himself. And do not take [these] messages of God in a frivolous spirit; and remember the blessings with which God has graced you, and all the revelation and the wisdom which He has bestowed on you from on high in order to admonish you thereby; and remain conscious of God, and know that God has full knowledge of everything.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/238.mp3","surahId":2,"words":[{"id":86366,"position":1,"arabic":"وَإِذَا","translation":"এবং যখন","audioUrl":"wbw/002_231_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86367,"position":2,"arabic":"طَلَّقْتُمُ","translation":"তোমরা তালাক দাও","audioUrl":"wbw/002_231_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86368,"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلنِّسَآءَ","translation":"স্ত্রীদেরকে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_231_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86369,"position":4,"arabic":"فَبَلَغْنَ","translation":"তারা অতঃপর পৌঁছে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_231_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86370,"position":5,"arabic":"أَجَلَهُنَّ","translation":"তাদের মেয়াদে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_231_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86371,"position":6,"arabic":"فَأَمْسِكُوهُنَّ","translation":"তাদেরকে রেখে দাও তখন","audioUrl":"wbw/002_231_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86372,"position":7,"arabic":"بِمَعْرُوفٍ","translation":"ন্যায়সঙ্গতভাবে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_231_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86373,"position":8,"arabic":"أَوْ","translation":"অথবা","audioUrl":"wbw/002_231_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86374,"position":9,"arabic":"سَرِّحُوهُنَّ","translation":"তাদের মুক্ত করে দাও","audioUrl":"wbw/002_231_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86375,"position":10,"arabic":"بِمَعْرُوفٍۢ ۚ","translation":"ন্যায় সংগতভাবে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_231_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86377,"position":11,"arabic":"وَلَا","translation":"এবং না","audioUrl":"wbw/002_231_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86378,"position":12,"arabic":"تُمْسِكُوهُنَّ","translation":"তাদেরকে তোমরা আটকে রেখো","audioUrl":"wbw/002_231_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86379,"position":13,"arabic":"ضِرَارًۭا","translation":"ক্ষতির (উদ্দেশ্যে)","audioUrl":"wbw/002_231_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86380,"position":14,"arabic":"لِّتَعْتَدُوا۟ ۚ","translation":"বাড়াবাড়ি করার জন্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_231_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86382,"position":15,"arabic":"وَمَن","translation":"এবং যে কেউ","audioUrl":"wbw/002_231_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86383,"position":16,"arabic":"يَفْعَلْ","translation":"করবে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_231_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86384,"position":17,"arabic":"ذَٰلِكَ","translation":"এটা","audioUrl":"wbw/002_231_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86385,"position":18,"arabic":"فَقَدْ","translation":"তাহলে নিশ্চয়ই","audioUrl":"wbw/002_231_020.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86386,"position":19,"arabic":"ظَلَمَ","translation":"অবিচার করবে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_231_021.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86387,"position":20,"arabic":"نَفْسَهُۥ ۚ","translation":"তারা নিজের (উপর)","audioUrl":"wbw/002_231_022.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86389,"position":21,"arabic":"وَلَا","translation":"এবং না","audioUrl":"wbw/002_231_024.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86390,"position":22,"arabic":"تَتَّخِذُوٓا۟","translation":"তোমরা গ্রহণ করো","audioUrl":"wbw/002_231_025.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86391,"position":23,"arabic":"ءَايَـٰتِ","translation":"নিদর্শনাবলীকে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_231_026.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86392,"position":24,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ","translation":"আল্লাহর","audioUrl":"wbw/002_231_027.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86393,"position":25,"arabic":"هُزُوًۭا ۚ","translation":"ঠাট্টাতামাশার বস্তু হিসেবে হিসেবে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_231_028.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86395,"position":26,"arabic":"وَٱذْكُرُوا۟","translation":"এবং তোমরা স্মরণ করো","audioUrl":"wbw/002_231_030.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86396,"position":27,"arabic":"نِعْمَتَ","translation":"অনুগ্রহকে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_231_031.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86397,"position":28,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ","translation":"আল্লাহর","audioUrl":"wbw/002_231_032.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86398,"position":29,"arabic":"عَلَيْكُمْ","translation":"তোমাদের উপর","audioUrl":"wbw/002_231_033.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86399,"position":30,"arabic":"وَمَآ","translation":"এবং যা","audioUrl":"wbw/002_231_034.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86400,"position":31,"arabic":"أَنزَلَ","translation":"অবতীর্ণ করেছেন","audioUrl":"wbw/002_231_035.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86401,"position":32,"arabic":"عَلَيْكُم","translation":"তোমাদের উপর","audioUrl":"wbw/002_231_036.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86402,"position":33,"arabic":"مِّنَ","translation":"থেকে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_231_037.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86403,"position":34,"arabic":"ٱلْكِتَـٰبِ","translation":"কিতাব","audioUrl":"wbw/002_231_038.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86404,"position":35,"arabic":"وَٱلْحِكْمَةِ","translation":"ও প্রজ্ঞা","audioUrl":"wbw/002_231_039.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86405,"position":36,"arabic":"يَعِظُكُم","translation":"তোমাদেরকে তিনি উপদেশ দিচ্ছেন","audioUrl":"wbw/002_231_040.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86406,"position":37,"arabic":"بِهِۦ ۚ","translation":"তা দিয়ে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_231_041.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86408,"position":38,"arabic":"وَٱتَّقُوا۟","translation":"এবং তোমরা ভয় করো","audioUrl":"wbw/002_231_043.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86409,"position":39,"arabic":"ٱللَّهَ","translation":"আল্লাহকে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_231_044.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86410,"position":40,"arabic":"وَٱعْلَمُوٓا۟","translation":"এবং তোমরা জেনে রাখো","audioUrl":"wbw/002_231_045.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86411,"position":41,"arabic":"أَنَّ","translation":"যে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_231_046.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86412,"position":42,"arabic":"ٱللَّهَ","translation":"আল্লাহ","audioUrl":"wbw/002_231_047.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86413,"position":43,"arabic":"بِكُلِّ","translation":"সব সম্পর্কে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_231_048.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86414,"position":44,"arabic":"شَىْءٍ","translation":"কিছুর","audioUrl":"wbw/002_231_049.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86415,"position":45,"arabic":"عَلِيمٌۭ","translation":"খুব অবহিত","audioUrl":"wbw/002_231_050.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86416,"position":46,"arabic":"٢٣١","translation":"(২৩১)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":232,"arabic":"وَإِذَا طَلَّقْتُمُ ٱلنِّسَآءَ فَبَلَغْنَ أَجَلَهُنَّ فَلَا تَعْضُلُوهُنَّ أَن يَنكِحْنَ أَزْوَٰجَهُنَّ إِذَا تَرَٰضَوْا۟ بَيْنَهُم بِٱلْمَعْرُوفِ ۗ ذَٰلِكَ يُوعَظُ بِهِۦ مَن كَانَ مِنكُمْ يُؤْمِنُ بِٱللَّهِ وَٱلْيَوْمِ ٱلْءَاخِرِ ۗ ذَٰلِكُمْ أَزْكَىٰ لَكُمْ وَأَطْهَرُ ۗ وَٱللَّهُ يَعْلَمُ وَأَنتُمْ لَا تَعْلَمُونَ","translation":"And when you divorce women, and they have come to the end of their waiting-term, hinder them not from marrying other men if they have agreed with each other in a fair manner. This is an admonition unto every one of you who believes in God and the Last Day; it is the most virtuous [way] for you, and the cleanest. And God knows, whereas you do not know.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/239.mp3","surahId":2,"words":[{"id":86417,"position":1,"arabic":"وَإِذَا","translation":"এবং যখন","audioUrl":"wbw/002_232_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86418,"position":2,"arabic":"طَلَّقْتُمُ","translation":"তালাক দাও তোমরা","audioUrl":"wbw/002_232_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86419,"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلنِّسَآءَ","translation":"স্ত্রীদেরকে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_232_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86420,"position":4,"arabic":"فَبَلَغْنَ","translation":"অতঃপর তারা পৌঁছে যায়","audioUrl":"wbw/002_232_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86421,"position":5,"arabic":"أَجَلَهُنَّ","translation":"তাদের মেয়াদে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_232_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86422,"position":6,"arabic":"فَلَا","translation":"না তখন","audioUrl":"wbw/002_232_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86423,"position":7,"arabic":"تَعْضُلُوهُنَّ","translation":"তাদেরকে বাধা দিয়ো","audioUrl":"wbw/002_232_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86424,"position":8,"arabic":"أَن","translation":"যে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_232_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86425,"position":9,"arabic":"يَنكِحْنَ","translation":"তারা বিয়ে করতে চায়","audioUrl":"wbw/002_232_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86426,"position":10,"arabic":"أَزْوَٰجَهُنَّ","translation":"তাদের (পূর্বের) স্বামীকে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_232_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86427,"position":11,"arabic":"إِذَا","translation":"যখন","audioUrl":"wbw/002_232_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86428,"position":12,"arabic":"تَرَٰضَوْا۟","translation":"তারা পরস্পর সম্মত হয়","audioUrl":"wbw/002_232_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86429,"position":13,"arabic":"بَيْنَهُم","translation":"তাদের মাঝে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_232_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86430,"position":14,"arabic":"بِٱلْمَعْرُوفِ ۗ","translation":"ন্যায় সংগত উপায়ে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_232_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86432,"position":15,"arabic":"ذَٰلِكَ","translation":"এটা","audioUrl":"wbw/002_232_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86433,"position":16,"arabic":"يُوعَظُ","translation":"উপদেশ দেয়া হচ্ছে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_232_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86434,"position":17,"arabic":"بِهِۦ","translation":"তার প্রতি","audioUrl":"wbw/002_232_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86435,"position":18,"arabic":"مَن","translation":"(তার জন্যে) যে কেউ","audioUrl":"wbw/002_232_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86436,"position":19,"arabic":"كَانَ","translation":"হয়","audioUrl":"wbw/002_232_020.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86437,"position":20,"arabic":"مِنكُمْ","translation":"তোমাদের মধ্যথেকে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_232_021.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86438,"position":21,"arabic":"يُؤْمِنُ","translation":"ঈমান এনে থাকে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_232_022.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86439,"position":22,"arabic":"بِٱللَّهِ","translation":"আল্লাহর উপর","audioUrl":"wbw/002_232_023.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86440,"position":23,"arabic":"وَٱلْيَوْمِ","translation":"ও দিনের","audioUrl":"wbw/002_232_024.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86441,"position":24,"arabic":"ٱلْـَٔاخِرِ ۗ","translation":"আখেরাতের","audioUrl":"wbw/002_232_025.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86443,"position":25,"arabic":"ذَٰلِكُمْ","translation":"এটা","audioUrl":"wbw/002_232_027.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86444,"position":26,"arabic":"أَزْكَىٰ","translation":"শুদ্ধতম পন্থা","audioUrl":"wbw/002_232_028.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86445,"position":27,"arabic":"لَكُمْ","translation":"তোমাদের জন্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_232_029.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86446,"position":28,"arabic":"وَأَطْهَرُ ۗ","translation":"ও পবিত্রতম","audioUrl":"wbw/002_232_030.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86448,"position":29,"arabic":"وَٱللَّهُ","translation":"এবং আল্লাহ","audioUrl":"wbw/002_232_032.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86449,"position":30,"arabic":"يَعْلَمُ","translation":"জানেন","audioUrl":"wbw/002_232_033.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86450,"position":31,"arabic":"وَأَنتُمْ","translation":"আর তোমরা","audioUrl":"wbw/002_232_034.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86451,"position":32,"arabic":"لَا","translation":"না","audioUrl":"wbw/002_232_035.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86452,"position":33,"arabic":"تَعْلَمُونَ","translation":"জান","audioUrl":"wbw/002_232_036.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86453,"position":34,"arabic":"٢٣٢","translation":"(২৩২)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":233,"arabic":"۞ وَٱلْوَٰلِدَٰتُ يُرْضِعْنَ أَوْلَٰدَهُنَّ حَوْلَيْنِ كَامِلَيْنِ ۖ لِمَنْ أَرَادَ أَن يُتِمَّ ٱلرَّضَاعَةَ ۚ وَعَلَى ٱلْمَوْلُودِ لَهُۥ رِزْقُهُنَّ وَكِسْوَتُهُنَّ بِٱلْمَعْرُوفِ ۚ لَا تُكَلَّفُ نَفْسٌ إِلَّا وُسْعَهَا ۚ لَا تُضَآرَّ وَٰلِدَةٌۢ بِوَلَدِهَا وَلَا مَوْلُودٌۭ لَّهُۥ بِوَلَدِهِۦ ۚ وَعَلَى ٱلْوَارِثِ مِثْلُ ذَٰلِكَ ۗ فَإِنْ أَرَادَا فِصَالًا عَن تَرَاضٍۢ مِّنْهُمَا وَتَشَاوُرٍۢ فَلَا جُنَاحَ عَلَيْهِمَا ۗ وَإِنْ أَرَدتُّمْ أَن تَسْتَرْضِعُوٓا۟ أَوْلَٰدَكُمْ فَلَا جُنَاحَ عَلَيْكُمْ إِذَا سَلَّمْتُم مَّآ ءَاتَيْتُم بِٱلْمَعْرُوفِ ۗ وَٱتَّقُوا۟ ٱللَّهَ وَٱعْلَمُوٓا۟ أَنَّ ٱللَّهَ بِمَا تَعْمَلُونَ بَصِيرٌۭ","translation":"And the [divorced] mothers may nurse their children for two whole years, if they wish to complete the period of nursing; and it is incumbent upon him who has begotten the child to provide in a fair manner for their sustenance and clothing. No human being shall be burdened with more than he is well able to bear: neither shall a mother be made to suffer because of her child, nor, because of his child, he who has begotten it. And the same duty rests upon the [father's] heir. And if both [parents] decide, by mutual consent and counsel, upon separation [of mother and child], they will incur no sin [thereby]; and if you decide to entrust your children to foster-mothers, you will incur no sin provided you ensure, in a fair manner, the safety of the child which you are handing over. But remain conscious of God, and know that God sees all that you do.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/240.mp3","surahId":2,"words":[{"id":86455,"position":1,"arabic":"۞ وَٱلْوَٰلِدَٰتُ","translation":"এবং মায়েরা","audioUrl":"wbw/002_233_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86456,"position":2,"arabic":"يُرْضِعْنَ","translation":"স্তন্য পান করাবে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_233_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86457,"position":3,"arabic":"أَوْلَـٰدَهُنَّ","translation":"তাদের সন্তানদের","audioUrl":"wbw/002_233_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86458,"position":4,"arabic":"حَوْلَيْنِ","translation":"দু’বছর","audioUrl":"wbw/002_233_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86459,"position":5,"arabic":"كَامِلَيْنِ ۖ","translation":"পূর্ণ","audioUrl":"wbw/002_233_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86461,"position":6,"arabic":"لِمَنْ","translation":"তার জন্য যে (বাপ)","audioUrl":"wbw/002_233_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86462,"position":7,"arabic":"أَرَادَ","translation":"চায়","audioUrl":"wbw/002_233_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86463,"position":8,"arabic":"أَن","translation":"যে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_233_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86464,"position":9,"arabic":"يُتِمَّ","translation":"পূর্ণ করবে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_233_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86465,"position":10,"arabic":"ٱلرَّضَاعَةَ ۚ","translation":"স্তন্যপান করানোর সময়","audioUrl":"wbw/002_233_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86467,"position":11,"arabic":"وَعَلَى","translation":"এবং (দায়িত্ব তার) উপর","audioUrl":"wbw/002_233_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86468,"position":12,"arabic":"ٱلْمَوْلُودِ","translation":"যার নবজাতক","audioUrl":"wbw/002_233_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86469,"position":13,"arabic":"لَهُۥ","translation":"জন্য","audioUrl":"wbw/002_233_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86470,"position":14,"arabic":"رِزْقُهُنَّ","translation":"তাদের (অর্থাৎ মাদের) জীবিকা","audioUrl":"wbw/002_233_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":86471,"position":15,"arabic":"وَكِسْوَتُهُنَّ","translation":"ও তাদের পোশাকের","audioUrl":"wbw/00